import React from 'react'
import Router from 'next/router'
import Link from 'next/link'

function index() {
    return ( <
        div >
        <
        button onClick = {
            () => {
                Router.push('/')
            }
        } >
        跳转到首页 <
        /button>
        宿建德江 <
        Link href = '/about' >
        <
        a >
        跳转到关于页面 <
        /a> <
        /Link> <
        /div>
    )
}

export default index
